”Alexa, tell me a joke from geeky jokes.”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: geeky jokes
des: Geeky Jokes gives Alexa the power to give you a joke or meme on command. Can be used for when you're feeling down or just want to impress your mates. It has no special requirements and will show you the memes on the Alexa app. Have fun!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
